OL,5, A company which ran children's homes   
OL,6, where residents were systemically      
OL,7, abused also failed to prevent adults   
OL,8, being harmed, BBC News has learned.    
OL,10,FAn investigation found 99 cases of     
OL,11,Fabuse at a Doncaster home for          
OL,12,Fvulnerable adults in 2010. One worker  
OL,13,Feven ordered a Taser to use there.     
OL,15,FThe care home company - Hesley - said  
OL,16,Fimprovements were made at the time.    
OL,18,FBut children at other Hesley homes were
OL,19,Flater reported to have been punched,   
OL,20,Fkicked and fed chillies.               
